ent-Z14STBrokenBed1 = broken wooden bed
    .desc = A relic of long-gone days, when life still flourished in this abandoned place. Its massive but cracked wooden beams, coated in dust and cobwebs, tell of when people slept here, dreamed, and perhaps even hoped for better.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STBrokenBed10 = broken iron bed
    .desc = A relic of the past, holding within it the spirit of its time and history. Its massive frame, once sturdy and reliable, is now covered in rust and dust — proof of long years of abandonment. The iron bars it was assembled from are bent and broken in places, with some pieces missing entirely, leaving only a hint of its former integrity.
    .suffix = Z14

